<br>
Unfortunately, there are a lot of people that are only here for the lack of no-drop, and they are the ones you'll see using /shout as a defacto /ooc. Most folk here have shouts turned off now (shouts used to only carry over a limited range, and not echo through the whole zone).<br>
<br>
Greater Faydark ... /sigh Yeah, it's pretty bad. Get out. If you have PoP, go elsewhere posthaste! The Plane of Knowledge isn't much better - GFay in the sky, but with KEI/Temp/Virtue beggars. <br>
<br>
You're wondering about the unwritten rules, hmm? Well, I don't know if I know them, but if I have an ooc question, I usually give a shout along these lines: <br>
<br>
&quot;Could anyone spare a moment to answer a (ooc) question, please? Send word.&quot; <br>
<br>
I've noticed that most people can figure out that &quot;send word&quot; means &quot;send tell.&quot; That way, you're not shouting question and answer across the zone.<br>
<br>
Tells, for some, are always ooc, but not for others. When in doubt, stay in character or use (ooc: &lt;question here&gt;) to denote the break. <br>
<br>
I'm not sure if that helps much, heh. I'm sure others will add to this, and hopefully you'll find the answers you need. Once again, welcome! <p><!--EZCODE CENTER START--><div style="text-align:center"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://home.attbi.com/~subacca/kullgensig.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE BR START--><br /><!--EZCODE BR END--><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong><!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-family:times;font-size:x-small;">Child of Innoruuk - Student of Thule</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></div><!--EZCODE CENTER END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/bfirionavie.showUserPublicProfile?gid=pazilla>Pazilla</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(5/10/03 3:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm9.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1541.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: New to Firiona Vie and Firiona Vie board</span><hr size=1> Thank you.  I left GFay. I had to turn off shout ooc and auction just to hear myself think.  I though about shouting Stop yelling!  With all the noise you are making, I can't hear approaching orcs!  Freeport folks are a lot quieter. <p>Panzilla Gatecrasher,45 Beastlord<br>
